---
import { Section, H1, H2, H3, P, Image, Icon, Button } from "ui";
---

<!-- Product -->
<Section name="product-card">
  <H1 class="text-primary hidden">
    Сухари панировочные Панко (Panko) ТМ "Yakimal", 1 кг
  </H1>

  <div class="product-card__img group">
    <div class="product-card__swiper">
      <div class="swiper">
        <div class="swiper-wrapper">
          <div
            class="swiper-slide"
            data-fancybox="product"
            data-src="/assets/img/our-products/2.png"
          >
            <Image src="our-products/2.png" />
          </div>
          <div
            class="swiper-slide"
            data-fancybox="product"
            data-src="/assets/img/our-products/1.png"
          >
            <Image src="our-products/1.png" />
          </div>
          <div
            class="swiper-slide"
            data-fancybox="product"
            data-src="/assets/img/our-products/2.png"
          >
            <Image src="our-products/2.png" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="product-card__swiper-nav">
        <div class="btn-prev"></div>
        <div class="btn-next"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="product-card__img-label">おいしい</div>
  </div>

  <div class="product-card__text group">
    <H1 class="text-primary">
      Сухари панировочные Панко (Panko) ТМ "Yakimal", 1 кг
    </H1>
    <P>
      Идеальный выбор для создания хрустящей, воздушной корочки, которая делает
      блюда особенно аппетитными. Панко отличаются легкой, хлопьевидной
      структурой, благодаря чему они впитывают меньше масла при жарке и создают
      равномерный, хрустящий слой.
      <br /><br />
      Этот продукт широко используется в японской и европейской кухне для приготовления
      темпуры, котлет, креветок, рыбы, курицы и овощей. Панировочные сухари Yakimal
      изготовлены из отборного пшеничного хлеба без лишних добавок, что гарантирует
      натуральный вкус и отличное качество. Подходит для ресторанного и домашнего
      использования, обеспечивая профессиональный результат в каждом блюде.
    </P>

    <Button
      variant="secondary"
      ru="Запросить оптовый прайс-лист"
      data-modal="callback"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="product-card__options group">
    <div class="product-card__options-title">Другие варианты товара</div>
    <div class="product-card__options-list">
      {
        Array.from({ length: 3 }).map((_, index) => (
          <div class="product">
            <a href="/product" class="product__link" />

            <div class="product__img">
              <Image src={`products/1.png`} />
            </div>
            <div class="product__content">
              <div class="product__content-title">
                Сухари панировочные Панко (Panko) ТМ "Yakimal", 10 кг
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </div>
</Section>

<style lang="scss" is:global>
  @use "scss/helpers" as *;

  .product-card {
    position: relative;

    .container {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: rem(700) 1fr;
      gap: rem(50) rem(80);

      @include media("3xl") {
        grid-template-columns: rem(600) 1fr;
      }
      @include media("2xl") {
        grid-template-columns: rem(500) 1fr;
        gap: rem(40);
      }
      @include media("xl") {
        grid-template-columns: rem(400) 1fr;
        gap: rem(30);
      }
      @include media(rem(980)) {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    .text-h1 {
      &.hidden {
        display: none;
      }

      @include media("3xl") {
        font-size: rem(40);
      }
      @include media("xl") {
        font-size: rem(32);
      }
      @include media("lg") {
        font-size: rem(24);
      }
      @include media(rem(980)) {
        display: none;

        &.hidden {
          display: block;
        }
      }
      @include media("xs") {
        font-size: rem(18);
      }
    }

    &__img {
      grid-row-start: span 2;
      gap: rem(10);

      @include media("2xl") {
        width: 100%;
        grid-row-start: unset;
      }

      &-label {
        color: var(--primary);
        font-size: clamp(2rem, -0.1429rem + 3.3482vw, 3.875rem);
        font-weight: 500;
        font-family: var(--font-monserrat);

        @include media(rem(980)) {
          display: none;
        }
      }
    }

    &__swiper {
      --size: #{rem(700)};
      margin-top: rem(50);
      position: relative;
      min-width: var(--size);
      width: var(--size);
      height: var(--size);
      background: url("/assets/img/bg-circle.png") center/cover no-repeat;
      border-radius: 50%;

      @include media("3xl") {
        --size: #{rem(600)};
      }
      @include media("2xl") {
        --size: #{rem(500)};
      }
      @include media("xl") {
        margin-top: 0;
        --size: #{rem(400)};
      }
      @include media(rem(980)) {
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      @include media("xs") {
        --size: #{rem(345)};
      }
      @include media(rem(360)) {
        --size: #{rem(320)};
      }

      &::before,
      &::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        pointer-events: none;
      }

      &::after {
        top: 18%;
        right: rem(10);
        height: rem(14);
        width: rem(156);
        background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg width="158" height="8" viewBox="0 0 158 8" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M1 5L2 4C5.86599 0.134006 12.134 0.134006 16 4V4C19.866 7.86599 26.134 7.86599 30 4V4C33.866 0.134006 40.134 0.134006 44 4V4C47.866 7.86599 54.134 7.86599 58 4V4C61.866 0.134006 68.134 0.134006 72 4V4C75.866 7.86599 82.134 7.86599 86 4V4C89.866 0.134006 96.134 0.134006 100 4V4C103.866 7.86599 110.134 7.86599 114 4V4C117.866 0.134006 124.134 0.134006 128 4V4C131.866 7.86599 138.134 7.86599 142 4V4C145.866 0.134006 152.134 0.134007 156 4L157 5" stroke="%23C5594D" stroke-width="2" /></svg>')
          center/contain no-repeat;

        @include media("xl") {
          transform: translateX(25%) scale(0.6);
        }
      }

      .swiper {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        overflow: visible;
      }

      .swiper-slide {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: flex-start;
        opacity: 0 !important;

        &-active {
          opacity: 1 !important;
        }

        img {
          margin-top: -20%;
          width: 100%;
          height: 100%;
          object-fit: contain;
          cursor: zoom-in;
        }
      }

      &-nav {
        position: absolute;
        bottom: rem(50);
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        z-index: 2;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: flex-start;
        gap: rem(200);

        @include media("xl") {
          gap: rem(120);
        }

        &::after {
          content: "";
          position: absolute;
          bottom: rem(15);
          right: rem(-60);
          width: rem(12);
          height: rem(153);
          background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg width="12" height="153" viewBox="0 0 12 153" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><circle cx="6" cy="6" r="6" fill="%23C5594D" /><circle cx="6" cy="53" r="6" fill="%23C5594D" /><circle cx="6" cy="100" r="6" fill="%23C5594D" /><circle cx="6" cy="147" r="6" fill="%23C5594D" /></svg>')
            center/contain no-repeat;
          pointer-events: none;

          @include media("xl") {
            bottom: rem(-10);
            right: rem(-40);
            transform: scale(0.6);
          }
        }
      }

      .btn-prev,
      .btn-next {
        width: rem(120);
        height: rem(20);
        background: url("/assets/img/icons/arrow-right.svg") center/contain
          no-repeat;

        @include media("xl") {
          width: rem(74);
          height: rem(12);
        }

        &.swiper-button-disabled {
          background: url("/assets/img/icons/arrow-right-disabled.svg")
            center/contain no-repeat;
          cursor: not-allowed;
        }
      }

      .btn-prev {
        transform: rotate(180deg);
      }
    }

    &__info {
      flex-grow: 1;
      gap: rem(50);
    }

    &__text {
      width: 100%;
      gap: rem(25);
    }

    &__options {
      width: 100%;
      gap: rem(60);

      @include media("2xl") {
        grid-column-start: span 2;
      }
      @include media(rem(980)) {
        margin-top: rem(30);
        grid-column-start: span 1;
      }
      @include media("sm") {
        gap: rem(40);
      }

      &-title {
        position: relative;
        color: var(--primary);
        font-size: rem(24);
        text-transform: uppercase;

        @include media("3xl") {
          font-size: rem(20);
        }
        @include media("xs") {
          font-size: rem(16);
        }

        &::after {
          content: "";
          margin-left: rem(20);
          display: inline-block;
          width: rem(156);
          height: rem(14);
          background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg width="265" height="13" viewBox="0 0 265 13" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M2 8.14286L3.67308 6.5C10.1754 0.115099 20.5938 0.1151 27.0962 6.5V6.5C33.5985 12.8849 44.0169 12.8849 50.5192 6.5V6.5C57.0216 0.1151 67.44 0.1151 73.9423 6.5V6.5C80.4447 12.8849 90.863 12.8849 97.3654 6.5V6.5C103.868 0.1151 114.286 0.1151 120.788 6.5V6.5C127.291 12.8849 137.709 12.8849 144.212 6.5V6.5C150.714 0.1151 161.132 0.1151 167.635 6.5V6.5C174.137 12.8849 184.555 12.8849 191.058 6.5V6.5C197.56 0.1151 207.978 0.1151 214.481 6.5V6.5C220.983 12.8849 231.401 12.8849 237.904 6.5V6.5C244.406 0.1151 254.825 0.1151 261.327 6.5L263 8.14286" stroke="%23C5594D" stroke-width="3"/></svg>')
            center/contain no-repeat;

          @include media("xs") {
            margin-left: rem(12);
            width: rem(80);
            height: rem(8);
          }
        }
      }

      &-list {
        width: 100%;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: rem(60) rem(20);

        @include media("sm") {
          grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
          gap: rem(40) rem(12);

          .product__content-title {
            font-size: rem(12);
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
</style>
